	"changelog": "\n* Brought the add-on back to life\n* Redeveloped the add-on from scratch\n* Added the ability to automatically detect your current location, which is enabled by default\n\t* Note: This feature may not be perfectly accurate in all cases\n\t* For better accuracy, you can use a geographic location app on your phone and manually enter the latitude and longitude in the settings\n\t* You must disable the automatic location detection feature to manually edit these geographic coordinates\n* Removed the country and city selection fields due to inaccuracies\n* Changed the data provider to retrieve cleaner results\n* Results are now displayed inside a readable text field\n* Implemented data caching to provide instant results when checking prayer times again\n\t* This cache resets automatically when you restart NVDA or press OK in the settings dialog\n* Added German translation\n* Added README files for Arabic, English, and German\n* Minor bug fixes and performance improvements\n",
